Description: Population residing in urban areas for each year (2000, 2010, 2020, 2030), derived by multiplying urbanLayer and populationLayer
Population on land that became urban in the last 10 years (e.g., 2010–2020, 2020–2030)
Population on land that became urban in the last 20 years (e.g., 2000–2020, 2010–2030)
Population on land that lost its urban status in the last 10 years (e.g., urban in 2010, non-urban in 2020)
Population on land that lost its urban status in the last 20 years (e.g., urban in 2000, non-urban in 2020)
Population change over specified time periods (e.g., 2000–2020, 2010–2020, 2010–2030, 2020–2030)
Population change for areas that were urban in the earlier year (y1) but non-urban in the later year (y2)  (e.g., 2000–2020, 2010–2020, 2010–2030, 2020–2030)
Population change for areas that were non-urban in the earlier year (y1) but urban in the later year (y2)  (e.g., 2000–2020, 2010–2020, 2010–2030, 2020–2030)
Population change for areas that remained urban across both years (y1 and y2)  (e.g., 2000–2020, 2010–2020, 2010–2030, 2020–2030)
